  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Prospective trial which includes instillation of intravesical hyaluronic acid in an attempt
      to reduce the incidence of urinary tract infections in patients after orthotopic neobladder
      reconstruction.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
